<br>
What if priest classes (who draw their power from a god) were actually influenced by the power of that god?<br>
<br>
IE if you kill innoruuk, all priests of Tunare get FT2 for the next week. Etc.<br>
Int classes be unaffected, as our power is inherent.<br>
<br>
Imho the results should always be positive ... having a mana drain because your god was killed would suck. But as long as the effects were good ones, it would be cool for the upper teir game to have an impact on the young adventurers.<br>
<br>
As a side note, I think you should be able to change your religions in EQ. It's just plain dumb that you can't.<br>
<br>
